# VHS tape — "One command to diagnose your entire agent setup"
# Shows the doctor command — instant environment diagnostics.

Output doctor.gif
Output doctor.mp4

Set Theme "Dracula"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1100
Set Height 600
Set Padding 28
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set WindowBarSize 40
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 400ms

Type "# Is your environment ready? One command to find out."
Enter
Sleep 1500ms

Type "npx @agentskit/cli doctor"
Sleep 400ms
Enter

Sleep 4000ms
